  <body>

  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nottingham_prognostic_index">Nottingham Prognostic Index</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nottingham_prognostic_index">Nottingham Prognostic Index</xref>
 is (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nottingham_prognostic_index">NPI</xref>
) a formula used by 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONALS</xref>
 to give them a general idea of how well treatment may work for a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
 with breast cancer and how long the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
 may live.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_nottingham_prognostic_index_score">NOTTINGHAM PROGNOSTIC INDEX SCORE</xref>
 is calculated using:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_tumour">Tumour</xref>
            <p>size in centimetres</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Histologic grade</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Number of positive axillary lymph nodes.</p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>

</body>
